\begin_inset Formula $e^{E}$
\end_inset

, what can be done to: (1) Keep the interest rate stable, (2) keep the exchange
 rate stable?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The entire curve will shift right
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
